                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>kind enough, to give place<lb/> in the <sic>colums</sic>, of your paper<lb/> I also\n                send you herewith<lb/> a Copy, of a Barmizwa<lb/> Speech, of a Nephew, of mine,<lb/>\n                which I would also like,<lb/> to see published, in your<lb/> valuable paper</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I remain yours respectfully</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">Myer Stern</persName>\n            </p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
